o.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475472cfc765ab45bb74c0547ab55639b913c8aa","tid":308192,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:24:28.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da58daa5737beb7699dcf270297ff2c51f1484da","tid":308192,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7cbd3a13dd7e7a61ad4612a791dec16ec76e1a","tid":308192,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:38:20.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a31e32e7e1dc89ebc85dab0b9d1710296426f8","tid":308192,"uid":34129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"search個filename咪得囉<br />\n唔得喺finder度揀all files"},{"pid":"ffad99cd410ba4856d83852d5613a543a5c4549e","tid":308192,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>search個filename咪得囉<br />\n唔得喺finder度揀all files</blockquote><br />\n有試過啊<br />\n就係連search foler name都無<br />\n所以先唔知邊度出問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98195a4001cf37581026b2b3673d3045da5bc4d","tid":308192,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>search個filename咪得囉<br />\n唔得喺finder度揀all files</blockquote><br />\n有試過啊<br />\n就係連search folder name都無<br />\n所以先唔知邊度出問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0e34b37d27843ca549ddd26eb5477a57f3f3a67